{{!
    @template mod_scorecard/template_warnings_confirmation_form

    Confirmation form rendered below the warnings block when the import
    helper returns state='warnings'. POSTs back to template_import.php with
    the original JSON content base64-encoded in pendingjson, plus
    confirmwarnings=1 to authorise the import. sesskey defends from CSRF.

    Context variables required:
    * action        - Form action URL (template_import.php).
    * cmid          - Course module id.
    * pendingjson   - base64-encoded original JSON template content.
    * sesskey       - Current session key.
    * cancelurl     - URL to manage.php to abandon the round-trip.
    * confirmlabel  - Lang string template:import:warnings:confirmbutton.
    * cancellabel   - Lang string template:import:warnings:cancellabel.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "action": "/mod/scorecard/template_import.php",
        "cmid": 42,
        "pendingjson": "eyJpdGVtcyI6W119",
        "sesskey": "abc123",
        "cancelurl": "/mod/scorecard/manage.php?id=42",
        "confirmlabel": "Yes, import anyway",
        "cancellabel": "Cancel"
    }
}}
<form method="post" action="{{action}}" class="scorecard-template-warnings-confirmation mb-3">
    <input type="hidden" name="cmid" value="{{cmid}}">
    <input type="hidden" name="pendingjson" value="{{pendingjson}}">
    <input type="hidden" name="confirmwarnings" value="1">
    <input type="hidden" name="sesskey" value="{{sesskey}}">
    <div class="scorecard-template-warnings-actions">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">{{confirmlabel}}</button>
        <a href="{{cancelurl}}" class="btn btn-link ms-2">{{cancellabel}}</a>
    </div>
</form>
